snippet.title: DJMAX RESPECT DLC CLAZZIQUAI EDITION - Trailer (ENG Sub)
snippet.description:
Take Clazziquai with DJMAX!
Today, RESPECT's DLC 'CLAZZIQUAI EDITION' is released.
Make new memories with #CLAZZIQUAI_EDITION #DLC!

[Official release]
▶ Date : 2017.12.21 AM 11:00 (UTC+9)
※ The store exposure time may be different.
▶ Target countries: Hong-Kong, Singapore, Taiwan, Malaysia, Indonesia, Thailand
▶ Price: 19,800 WON
▶ Format : DLC
▶ Bonus : First Kiss gear skin, CLAZZIQUAI EDITION UI skin
▶ Music composition : CLAZZIQUAI EDITION Song 22, RESPECT Neow song 1

[MUSIC LIST]
▶ CLAZZIQUAI EDITION
Come to Me, Color, Creator, Electronics, Flea, Freedom
Love Mode, The Night Stage, Forever
Closer, Fate, Here in the Moment, Lover (CE Style)
Tell Me, Urban Night, Proposed, Flower, Wolf, To You
Coastal Tempo, First Kiss, In My Heart, The Clear Blue Sky, Y (CE Style)

▶ New Song
Rising The Sonic - Dayz

▶ 1.10 Patch History
- ADD Dreadnought - EarBreaker

▶ Notes
The 1.10 patch is required so you can use DLC,
Please play after you get online patch.

#DJMAX #RESPECT #Clazziquai
#PS4 #musical_game #music_game #rhythm_game 
#release #SONY #SIEK #네오위즈 #NEOWIZ
